.\nWe say `self` is the congruence class root if `isSameExpr congr self`.\nThis field is initialized to `self` even if `e` is not an application.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode.congr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">ENode</span>.<span class=\"name\">congr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode\">ENode</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.lean#L266-L266","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode.root","line":266,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode.root","doc":"Root (aka canonical representative) of the equivalence class "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode.root\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">ENode</span>.<span class=\"name\">root</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode\">ENode</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.lean#L264-L264","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.ENode.